WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.360 --> 00:00:06.460
 Delicious Recipes 

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:14.040
 For the inner mortar of our fried 2 tablespoons of oil are taken into a suitable pan, 

00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:19.620
 Lightly roasted by adding 2 small small chopped onions. 

00:00:25.860 --> 00:00:30.380
 Then 400g minced meat is added to continue to roast. 

00:00:40.580 --> 00:00:43.040
 After the meat is roasted salt, 

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:44.560
 cumin, 

00:00:44.940 --> 00:00:47.360
 and mixed with black pepper 

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:49.640
 and the internal mortar is removed from the furnace. 

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:05.500
 150 ml water to the kneading dish for the dough, 

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:08.320
 150 ml milk, 

00:01:10.300 --> 00:01:12.840
 2 tablespoons of vinegar, 

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:15.960
 1 tablespoon deleting salt 

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:21.720
 and by slowly adding flour, the dough is kneaded. 

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:28.100
 About 4.5 to 5 cups of flour were used in this description. 

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:43.860
 After the dough is ready to be rested for 20 minutes. 

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:48.940
 The dough is divided into 2 pieces and the beans are formed. 

00:02:02.980 --> 00:02:10.020
 One of the noodles is opened with the help of the flour and taken aside. 

00:02:42.980 --> 00:02:46.080
 The other cloth opens in the same way. 

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:57.240
 Half of the 150g butter which we have already melted is poured on the dough and spread beautifully. 

00:03:07.620 --> 00:03:11.340
 Our second dough is covered and the remaining butter is spread. 

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:37.920
 They are wrapped in roll form. 

00:03:50.020 --> 00:03:54.060
 The roll is placed in a suitable container and covered with stretch film. 

00:03:57.660 --> 00:04:00.880
 half an hour in the refrigerator. 

00:04:09.580 --> 00:04:14.760
 The rolled roll is divided into slices, approximately 2 fingers wide. 

00:04:19.780 --> 00:04:22.040
 Slices open with a rolling pin. 

00:04:38.900 --> 00:04:42.960
 It is placed in the middle of the interior mortar and sealed in an envelope. 

00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:47.280
 and placed on the baking sheet such that the joint is at the bottom. 

00:05:01.060 --> 00:05:06.580
 After all dough is prepared, scrambled eggs are smeared on them. 

00:05:10.140 --> 00:05:15.500
 baked in pre-heated 180 degrees oven until golden brown. 

00:05:17.140 --> 00:05:21.440
 Fruits taken from the oven after the first heat can be served. 

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:31.660
 We recommend you to try this delicious pastry with its delicious inner mortar in the crispy dough. 

00:05:32.100 --> 00:05:34.720
 You're welcome to try. 

